                        <span class="result-label">Total New Interest</span>
                        <span class="result-value" id="new-total-interest" style="font-size: 0.9375rem;">$0</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="result-item">
                        <span class="result-label">Total New Cost (incl. fees)</span>
